{"type": "article", "id": 4325, "title": "Valentino & Piero Fornasetti 联名系列", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-12T07:50:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233330uphC6cDySa9rJXGH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t意大利奢侈品品牌 Valentino 日前邀请意大利设计大师 Piero Fornasetti ，联手为今年的假日季推出了一系列联名物件，包括太阳眼镜、凳子、方巾以及盘子，在本月 10 日纽约举行的 Valentino Sala Bianca 945 活动上正式发布。整个联名系列围绕「parallel vision」这一主题，将 Valentino 经典的迷彩设计元素与 Piero Fornasetti 最为擅长的人像创作风格进行融合。此外，双方还为这款太阳眼镜搭配设计了一款皮革材质的眼镜盒与一个木质的外包装。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233327aP47Wu5Ujsk1RlO6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052333273kx4heGY7ngmbvAQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233327rfmbWNBUgJhxFO46.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233328CqgH2tL6FArw5jJz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052333283cO8MxQt5Yyf91qG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052333297XREobZe5QOcpFUW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}